- "Positively rated" means an average rating greater than 3.5;
- "Commented on" means users have made more than one comment on the poll.

sql:
SELECT poll_id, rating
FROM poll_ratings
WHERE rating = (SELECT MAX(rating) FROM poll_ratings);
